WEBVTT

00:06.000 --> 00:12.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

03:00.847 --> 03:04.021
With the power vested in me
by nobody in particular...

03:04.226 --> 03:09.448
I hereby crown you Princess Kuda,
ruler of the seven seas.

03:43.348 --> 03:47.353
Oh, thank you.
Thank you, my loyal subjects.

03:48.812 --> 03:53.113
Ladies and jellyfish,
let us celebrate my coronation...

03:53.316 --> 03:55.193
with a royal ball.

03:55.902 --> 03:58.872
Let joy be unconfined!

03:59.072 --> 04:01.791
May I have this dance, milady?

04:01.992 --> 04:04.620
Charmed, I'm sure.

04:14.463 --> 04:16.966
- Lumina?
- Aah.

04:17.173 --> 04:19.142
- Uh-oh.
- Aah!

04:28.185 --> 04:30.608
Lumina?

04:31.188 --> 04:32.690
Lumina.

04:32.898 --> 04:34.525
What was that commotion?

04:34.941 --> 04:35.988
Um...

04:36.610 --> 04:40.331
Oh, we were just playing
coronation, Aunt Scylla.

04:45.911 --> 04:49.290
Were you using your
pearl magic outside?

04:49.498 --> 04:50.715
Um...

04:50.916 --> 04:53.419
Well, maybe, just a little.

04:53.752 --> 04:56.722
Lumina,
I've told you and told you...

04:56.922 --> 04:59.175
- keep your powers private.
- Powers private.

04:59.382 --> 05:01.976
I know, Aunt Scylla.
I'm sorry, really.

05:02.177 --> 05:04.225
You have a very special gift...

05:04.429 --> 05:05.851
but if word got out...

05:06.056 --> 05:09.356
Well, all kinds of bad people
might come looking for you.

05:09.559 --> 05:10.902
But I don't understand.

05:11.394 --> 05:13.647
Who's gonna see me way out here?

05:13.855 --> 05:15.277
You don't need to understand.

05:15.482 --> 05:18.031
Please, just do as I say.

05:21.488 --> 05:23.206
Hello, Kuda.

05:23.406 --> 05:26.000
Hi, Aunt Scylla. Ha, ha.

05:29.996 --> 05:32.124
Ah. Great.

05:32.332 --> 05:33.925
Now your aunt's mad.

05:34.125 --> 05:36.173
And I've got clam dents in my head.

05:36.378 --> 05:38.255
Oh, you look fine.

05:38.463 --> 05:42.184
Hmm. Except for your hair.

05:42.676 --> 05:44.474
Uh-oh.

05:49.850 --> 05:51.898
Hmm.

05:52.310 --> 05:53.937
Uh-uh.

06:03.488 --> 06:05.240
Hmm.

06:11.746 --> 06:15.000
No. Still not right.

06:19.337 --> 06:21.260
I think that's the one.

06:21.464 --> 06:24.183
Let's see.
You need something to wear.

06:45.196 --> 06:46.243
There.

06:46.448 --> 06:48.621
Now you look like a princess.

06:55.081 --> 06:56.628
Hmm?

07:07.928 --> 07:11.353
And now we both look
like princesses.

07:13.141 --> 07:16.361
I wonder what a real
princess looks like.

07:16.561 --> 07:17.813
Yeah.

07:18.021 --> 07:21.070
And the royal castle.

07:21.608 --> 07:24.657
And all the beautiful mermaids
and their elegant clothes.

07:24.861 --> 07:28.206
Can you imagine the dances
they must have there?

07:28.406 --> 07:32.206
Kuda, you think we'll ever
really get to see the castle?

07:32.410 --> 07:33.878
Maybe.

07:34.079 --> 07:35.877
Someday.

07:36.081 --> 07:39.085
I bet it's just the most
wonderful place ever.

07:39.292 --> 07:42.717
I bet everyone there
is happy all the time.

07:43.338 --> 07:45.340
Your Gracious Majesties.

07:45.757 --> 07:50.354
All I ask is that you consent to
appear in public just one night.

07:50.553 --> 07:52.351
Your subjects need you.

07:52.555 --> 07:54.478
Your kingdom needs you.

07:54.683 --> 07:56.105
Dare I say it...

07:58.019 --> 07:59.817
I need you.

08:00.021 --> 08:04.743
Caligo, as I've told you many
times, Queen Lorelei and I...

08:04.943 --> 08:07.492
Of course, of course.

08:07.696 --> 08:09.448
And like you...

08:09.656 --> 08:14.002
I am inconsolable over
the lost princess.

08:14.202 --> 08:17.923
But we simply must face the fact...

08:18.123 --> 08:21.423
that with you and the
queen having no heir...

08:21.626 --> 08:25.506
the kingdom will one day pass
to your nephew, my son.

08:26.798 --> 08:28.926
Hello, <i>Neocrinus decorus.</i>

08:29.134 --> 08:31.853
And how are we today? Aah!

08:36.433 --> 08:38.231
I'm afraid Caligo is right.

08:38.727 --> 08:40.775
Perhaps it is time.

08:40.979 --> 08:44.859
Excellent! And since he'll also
need to choose a suitable wife...

08:45.066 --> 08:46.989
we'll give a royal ball.

08:47.193 --> 08:49.491
We'll invite only the
most beautiful...

08:49.696 --> 08:52.245
and eligible young
mermaids of the kingdom...

08:52.449 --> 08:57.797
for a chance to be my son's queen.

08:59.497 --> 09:00.999
Huh?

09:02.709 --> 09:04.256
Aah!

09:12.761 --> 09:16.015
Aah, aah, aah...

09:20.268 --> 09:21.315
Oh.

09:21.519 --> 09:24.773
Perhaps we should
invite all the maidens.

09:24.981 --> 09:26.654
And throw in a door prize.

09:26.858 --> 09:29.407
Whoa. Ugh.

09:56.346 --> 09:59.316
Yoo-hoo!

10:07.982 --> 10:09.450
Hmm.

10:09.818 --> 10:10.865
Aah!

10:11.069 --> 10:12.161
Oh, dear me.

10:12.362 --> 10:15.866
Did I frighten you? Ha-ha-ha.

10:16.699 --> 10:18.827
Who are you? What do you want?

10:19.369 --> 10:24.626
I go by many names,
but you may call me Murray.

10:24.833 --> 10:30.556
I come bearing an eel-mail from
an old friend of yours, Caligo.

10:30.797 --> 10:33.266
Hey!

10:33.633 --> 10:34.680
Out!

10:38.888 --> 10:42.267
I admit tracking you down
was a particular challenge.

10:42.475 --> 10:46.070
But my Bottom Feeders
Network came through.

10:46.271 --> 10:47.898
All right, you've found me.

10:48.106 --> 10:49.574
What is it you want?

10:49.774 --> 10:52.948
Ah, that famous hag hospitality.

10:53.153 --> 10:54.530
A simple request, really.

10:54.737 --> 11:00.540
My employer is once again in need
of your, um, professional services.

11:00.743 --> 11:04.373
Services? What services?

11:04.581 --> 11:07.926
Caligo convinced His Majesty to open
up the castle for a royal ball...

11:08.126 --> 11:11.471
at which time the king will confer
the Pearl of the Sea medallion...

11:11.671 --> 11:13.514
onto Caligo's son.

11:13.715 --> 11:19.393
His Majesty will then toast the boy
from a cup of merberry nectar.

11:19.596 --> 11:22.816
- Which Caligo wants me to poison.
- Exactly.

11:23.016 --> 11:25.815
The king croaks, the son is
crowned, everybody wins.

11:26.019 --> 11:27.191
Well, maybe not the king.

11:27.395 --> 11:29.648
Don't you love a happy ending?

11:29.856 --> 11:34.202
Well, you can tell your employer that
I'm no longer in the poisoning business.

11:34.402 --> 11:36.245
So unless you're
interested in buying...

11:36.446 --> 11:41.043
some gill glistener or
scale brightener, get out!

11:41.492 --> 11:42.618
He said you'd say that.

11:42.827 --> 11:45.501
I am, therefore, authorised
to issue the following threat:

11:46.039 --> 11:50.294
Do it or I'll tell everyone you
killed the princess. Ha-ha-ha.

11:50.501 --> 11:51.923
You wouldn't dare.

11:52.128 --> 11:53.801
He said you'd say that too.

11:54.005 --> 11:56.474
I am, therefore,
authorised to respond:

11:56.674 --> 11:58.722
Would so.

12:00.595 --> 12:01.642
Fine.

12:01.846 --> 12:06.568
If it's poison Caligo wants,
it's poison he'll get.

12:09.562 --> 12:12.190
A wise decision.

12:12.398 --> 12:14.867
Here, you'll need this
invitation to the ball.

12:15.985 --> 12:19.740
We'll leave the sordid details
in your expert hands.

12:19.948 --> 12:24.545
After all, it's really
all in the execution...

12:24.744 --> 12:26.712
wouldn't you agree?

12:28.164 --> 12:30.758
Now, don't be late, 8 p.m.,
Saturday, at the castle.

12:30.959 --> 12:32.961
- Castle?
- Huh?

12:33.336 --> 12:34.838
What about the castle?

12:40.551 --> 12:43.350
Well, well. And who is this?

12:43.763 --> 12:45.857
- Hmm.
- Hi. I'm Lum...

12:46.057 --> 12:48.105
- Late again for dinner.
- Aah!

12:48.309 --> 12:50.403
Our guest was just leaving.

12:50.603 --> 12:51.900
But, Aunt Scylla...

12:52.272 --> 12:53.569
Aunt Scylla?

12:53.773 --> 12:56.117
I assumed you lived alone.

12:56.317 --> 13:00.117
- Maybe I should...
- You assumed wrong. Get out!

13:00.613 --> 13:01.990
Aah!

13:05.410 --> 13:07.253
Hmm.

13:15.461 --> 13:17.429
Aunt Scylla.

13:20.174 --> 13:21.847
Hey!

13:24.262 --> 13:27.482
What was your friend talking about?
Did he mean the royal castle?

13:27.682 --> 13:28.899
Are you going there?

13:29.100 --> 13:30.693
Can I go? Can I go? Can I go?

13:30.893 --> 13:33.191
- Please?
- Lumina.

13:33.396 --> 13:36.741
I heard it has golden doors
and pearl chandeliers...

13:36.941 --> 13:39.364
and a beautiful throne,
and it must be wonderful.

13:39.569 --> 13:43.164
And I've always wanted to
go there, and so does Kuda.

13:43.364 --> 13:46.493
Absolutely not. I've told you
how dangerous the journey is.

13:46.701 --> 13:51.298
I do it to sell my potions, but it's
far too risky for a young girl alone.

13:51.497 --> 13:53.591
But I wouldn't be alone.

13:54.500 --> 13:56.252
I'd have you. And Kuda.

13:56.461 --> 13:58.213
And burning fire coral...

13:58.421 --> 14:01.391
and vampire squid and
poisonous stonefish.

14:02.842 --> 14:07.598
Lumina, neither of you has ever
been an inch outside this reef.

14:07.805 --> 14:08.852
Believe me...

14:09.057 --> 14:12.482
you wouldn't last two seconds,
even with me to keep an eye on you.

14:12.685 --> 14:15.655
- But...
- It's out of the question.

14:19.525 --> 14:22.404
Uh, I think that's a "no."

14:22.612 --> 14:25.832
I kind of stopped listening
after vampire squid.

14:29.118 --> 14:30.745
Now, you be good.

14:30.953 --> 14:32.580
I'll be back in a few days.

14:32.789 --> 14:36.919
And please, both of you,
stick close to home.

14:37.335 --> 14:38.712
Mm-hm.

14:38.920 --> 14:41.343
That's a good girl.

14:43.091 --> 14:44.138
Bye!

14:44.509 --> 14:46.352
Goodbye.

14:59.482 --> 15:02.452
I guess we're never gonna
get to see the castle, Kuda.

15:05.905 --> 15:09.705
Hey, wanna play tail tag? Huh?

15:09.909 --> 15:11.661
- You're it.
- Heh.

15:15.832 --> 15:16.879
Huh?

15:22.797 --> 15:25.721
Hmm. What's this?

15:28.636 --> 15:30.263
It's an invitation.

15:30.471 --> 15:32.314
She's not just going to the castle.

15:32.515 --> 15:35.189
She's invited to a royal ball.

15:36.561 --> 15:39.690
And she can't get in without this.

15:39.897 --> 15:41.069
Huh?

15:41.649 --> 15:44.368
Aunt Scylla! You forgot your...!

15:49.407 --> 15:51.125
Hmm.

15:56.164 --> 16:01.967
Kuda, we really should bring
this to her, don't you think?

16:02.670 --> 16:04.388
No, I don't think.

16:04.589 --> 16:07.012
Well, after all, she'll need
it to get into the ball.

16:07.216 --> 16:09.469
So when you think about it...

16:09.677 --> 16:12.476
it's really our duty
to go after her.

16:12.680 --> 16:15.183
All the way to the
castle if we have to.

16:15.391 --> 16:16.813
Lumina, no!

16:17.018 --> 16:18.611
She'll be furious.

16:18.811 --> 16:20.154
Were you listening to Scylla?

16:20.354 --> 16:22.027
- The dangerous journey?
- Psh.

16:22.190 --> 16:25.160
You mean the burning whatchamacallit
and the poisonous thingamapoo?

16:25.359 --> 16:29.159
It was the burning fire coral
and poisonous stonefish.

16:29.363 --> 16:32.116
Don't you see?
This is our big chance.

16:32.325 --> 16:34.043
Oh, Kuda, we've got to go.

16:34.243 --> 16:35.369
We've just got to.

16:35.578 --> 16:38.297
But... But... But...

16:38.748 --> 16:39.840
But... But... But...

16:40.041 --> 16:41.964
This has to be the right way.

16:43.920 --> 16:47.970
I've seen Aunt Scylla head this
way every time she goes to town.

16:48.758 --> 16:50.431
Unh.

16:51.928 --> 16:54.226
It's a dead end.

16:57.433 --> 16:59.026
Oh, darn. Oh, well, that's that.

16:59.227 --> 17:00.729
We gave it our best. Let's go home.

17:00.937 --> 17:04.066
Hmm. I just don't underst...

17:04.857 --> 17:06.450
Huh?

17:07.359 --> 17:08.703
Lumina.

17:09.694 --> 17:11.696
Wait for me!

17:20.455 --> 17:22.333
Oh, look, an opening.

17:22.541 --> 17:25.011
I bet that's her shortcut
through the coral.

17:25.211 --> 17:28.214
Follow me, Kuda. Don't be afraid.

17:28.422 --> 17:30.641
Make up your mind. I can't do both.

17:40.184 --> 17:45.657
Uh, Lumina, you do realise
we're inside a someone, right?

17:45.856 --> 17:48.484
Come on, Kuda. I bet the
end is right down here.

17:49.527 --> 17:52.326
Look at this. These are ribs.

17:52.530 --> 17:57.377
We're in a beast.
A big, huge... Uh-oh.

18:03.666 --> 18:05.168
Aah!

18:08.254 --> 18:09.676
This is not fun!

18:10.881 --> 18:12.098
Lumina!

18:12.300 --> 18:13.927
Swim!

18:14.135 --> 18:15.933
The invitation.

18:33.237 --> 18:34.659
Huh?

18:34.864 --> 18:36.036
Whoa!

18:40.953 --> 18:43.047
- Ha. Got it.
- Ahh.

18:43.247 --> 18:45.500
Okay, let's go.

18:51.380 --> 18:52.802
Oh, no.

18:55.176 --> 18:56.974
No, no, no!

18:57.595 --> 18:58.767
Oh, no!

19:09.774 --> 19:11.776
Know any more handy shortcuts?

19:11.984 --> 19:13.531
Aah. Oh, no.

19:13.736 --> 19:15.613
The invitation, it's gone.

19:15.821 --> 19:17.539
There.

19:17.865 --> 19:19.492
All right.

19:22.578 --> 19:24.000
A narwhal?

19:24.205 --> 19:27.175
- Now what?
- Come on, we just need to follow him.

19:27.375 --> 19:29.628
Here we go again.

19:32.672 --> 19:36.267
But, Father,
do I have to go to the ball?

19:36.467 --> 19:39.437
Yes, Fergie, because
it's being given for you.

19:39.637 --> 19:42.732
But I've told you,
I don't want to be king.

19:42.932 --> 19:46.152
I want to be a botanist.

19:46.352 --> 19:48.775
Forget about plants.

19:49.271 --> 19:53.492
You're going to be king and
that's the end of it, understood?

19:54.151 --> 19:57.405
Now, get back to
your waltz lessons.

19:57.613 --> 19:59.411
- Yes, sir.
- Hmph.

19:59.615 --> 20:03.119
Forgive me, <i>Neocrinus decorus.</i>

20:07.581 --> 20:08.628
Ah.

20:08.833 --> 20:11.256
The Pearl of the Sea medallion.

20:11.460 --> 20:13.588
- Soon it will be mine.
- Miss me?

20:13.796 --> 20:14.968
Aah!

20:15.172 --> 20:18.096
I wish you'd stop doing that!

20:18.300 --> 20:21.930
He, he. Me too.
But I don't think I can.

20:22.513 --> 20:24.811
Well? Did you find Scylla?

20:25.015 --> 20:28.019
I did, and she agreed to do it.

20:28.227 --> 20:29.945
Excellent.

20:30.146 --> 20:32.899
And once she's poisoned
the king at the ball...

20:33.107 --> 20:36.486
then I will rise up
in righteous fury...

20:36.694 --> 20:38.696
and finish off the old hag.

20:38.904 --> 20:41.874
Presto, I'm hailed as
a national hero...

20:42.074 --> 20:46.750
and my son is crowned
king of Seagundia.

20:46.954 --> 20:49.958
My, you have thought of everything.

20:50.166 --> 20:52.419
I make it my business to.

20:52.626 --> 20:59.180
And once my son is king, I will wield
the real power in the kingdom.

20:59.383 --> 21:05.732
And now comes the hard part,
finding someone to marry him.

21:05.931 --> 21:07.808
Perhaps you should talk to Scylla.

21:08.017 --> 21:11.146
You know, she has
quite a lovely niece.

21:11.645 --> 21:12.897
Aah!

21:13.105 --> 21:14.277
Niece?

21:14.482 --> 21:18.703
Goodness me,
did I fail to mention that?

21:19.236 --> 21:22.456
Blond, about 17 years old.

21:22.656 --> 21:25.455
Interesting coincidence,
don't you think?

21:25.659 --> 21:26.785
What?

21:26.994 --> 21:29.873
I'm guessing that's a "yes."

21:30.080 --> 21:31.127
Murray...

21:31.916 --> 21:34.044
bring me that girl.

21:34.251 --> 21:36.424
I want to ask her a few questions.

21:36.629 --> 21:38.597
Ha-ha-ha. Uh-huh.

21:44.470 --> 21:46.222
Hmm.

21:49.350 --> 21:53.230
This forest goes on forever.

21:53.437 --> 21:54.814
And it's getting kind of dark.

21:58.067 --> 21:59.535
Hey. There!

22:02.279 --> 22:03.496
Quick, after him!

22:16.961 --> 22:18.008
Lights?

22:18.212 --> 22:19.885
The city.

22:20.089 --> 22:22.933
Lumina, wait up!

22:25.594 --> 22:27.892
- Whoa.
- Aah!

22:34.895 --> 22:36.488
Huh?

23:00.337 --> 23:02.055
Oh, no.

23:08.429 --> 23:09.772
Aah!

23:12.016 --> 23:14.610
Oh, no. Aah!

23:16.812 --> 23:19.656
Uh, Lumina?

23:24.111 --> 23:25.203
Huh?

23:27.323 --> 23:30.167
Move away from the rock.

23:30.701 --> 23:31.827
What?

23:32.036 --> 23:35.290
Move away from the rock.

23:35.956 --> 23:37.003
Why?

23:42.087 --> 23:43.430
Huh?

23:45.174 --> 23:46.676
That's why.

23:46.884 --> 23:48.010
A stonefish.

23:48.218 --> 23:50.141
One of the most poisonous...

23:50.346 --> 23:52.098
The most poisonous!

23:52.306 --> 23:55.776
Make that the most
poisonous fish in the sea.

23:56.810 --> 23:58.153
That's right, lady.

23:58.354 --> 24:01.028
You are looking at the
face of certain doom!

24:01.231 --> 24:03.108
Nice to meet you, Mr. Doom.

24:03.317 --> 24:06.070
That is one powerful
voice you have.

24:07.988 --> 24:09.786
Aren't you gonna move it?

24:10.908 --> 24:12.751
I vote with him.

24:12.952 --> 24:14.329
Aren't you listening?

24:17.581 --> 24:22.963
Each one of my poisonous spikes
means a terrible, horrible end.

24:23.629 --> 24:24.881
Hmm.

24:35.140 --> 24:37.188
There. Much prettier.

24:38.143 --> 24:39.941
Hmm? Huh?

24:40.145 --> 24:43.115
What? What have you done to me?

24:44.441 --> 24:47.035
Yeah, what have you done to him?

24:47.236 --> 24:48.988
I just de-spiked your spikes.

24:49.196 --> 24:50.948
Now no one needs to
be scared of you.

24:51.156 --> 24:54.376
Oh. Great.

24:54.785 --> 24:56.253
Just great.

24:56.453 --> 24:58.672
Now what am I supposed to do?

24:58.872 --> 24:59.919
Just be nicer.

25:00.124 --> 25:01.751
Stop trying to frighten everyone.

25:01.959 --> 25:03.302
Get to know your fellow fish.

25:03.752 --> 25:05.595
Easy for you to say.

25:05.796 --> 25:08.049
But everyone runs from me.

25:08.257 --> 25:11.477
Once no one's afraid of you,
I bet you'll have loads of friends.

25:11.677 --> 25:12.724
I don't know.

25:12.928 --> 25:14.976
It all seems wrong for a stonefish.

25:15.180 --> 25:17.683
And I'm not so good
at friendliness.

25:17.891 --> 25:20.861
We're heading to the city.
There's lots of fish there, Mr. Doom.

25:21.061 --> 25:23.610
You could practise being
friendly on them.

25:24.898 --> 25:26.992
The name's Spike.

25:27.192 --> 25:30.822
- You don't mind me coming along?
- I'd be honoured.

25:32.156 --> 25:33.533
And I'd be nervous.

25:33.741 --> 25:36.244
But I'll give it a shot.

25:51.508 --> 25:54.227
Candygram!

25:54.511 --> 25:56.309
Eel Scout cookies!

26:06.523 --> 26:08.321
Aha.

26:08.525 --> 26:10.573
Garth, Wormwood.

26:20.996 --> 26:22.714
Let's go.

26:29.671 --> 26:31.173
Huh?

26:31.799 --> 26:33.096
Hmm.

26:35.177 --> 26:36.349
