on them every Tuesday. Mm-hm.

31:48.115 --> 31:49.207
- Bye-bye.
- Huh?

31:50.826 --> 31:52.954
Salon Du Mer.
Madame Ruckus speaking.

31:53.161 --> 31:56.836
